kde-service-menu-reimage (2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Advanced optimization for web
  * Compress in % (change quality)
  * Resize in % or square
  * Convert to all formats supported by ImageMagick
  * Convert to PDF or PDF/A-1
  * Convert to animated GIF
  * Convert to Base64
  * Convert to Greyscale
  * Sepia filter
  * Rotate
  * Overturn vertically/horizontally

 -- Giuseppe Benigno <giuseppe.benigno@gmail.com>  Mon, 30 Apr 2018 17:15:34 +0200

